---
// No external data needed
---

<section class="benefits" id="beneficios" aria-labelledby="ben-h">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="benefits__header">
      <p class="section-label fade-up" style="color:var(--cyan);">Beneficios</p>
      <h2 class="section-h2 fade-up" id="ben-h">Por qué tener agua purificada<br/>cambia el día a día</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="benefits__layout fade-up" role="list">
      <div class="ben-row1">
        <div class="ben-card ben-card--a" role="listitem">
          <div class="ben-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="44" height="44" viewBox="0 0 44 44" fill="none"><circle cx="22" cy="22" r="21" stroke="rgba(0,200,224,.4)" stroke-width="1"/><path d="M14 22h16M22 14v16" stroke="#00c8e0" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/><circle cx="22" cy="22" r="5" stroke="rgba(0,200,224,.5)" stroke-width="1"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="ben-card__title">Mejor sabor y olor</h3>
          <p class="ben-card__desc">Sin cloro, sin metales. El agua sabe como debe saber: limpia y natural.</p>
          <div class="ben-card__num" aria-hidden="true">01</div>
        </div>
        <div class="ben-card ben-card--b" role="listitem">
          <div class="ben-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="44" height="44" viewBox="0 0 44 44" fill="none"><path d="M22 6c0 0-14 16-14 25a14 14 0 0028 0c0-9-14-25-14-25z" stroke="#2c6faa" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M16 32a8 8 0 008-8" stroke="#00c8e0" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="ben-card__title">Ahorrás hasta 25x vs. embotellada</h3>
          <p class="ben-card__desc">Un equipo Puraqua produce agua purificada a una fracción del costo del agua en botella.</p>
          <div class="ben-card__num" aria-hidden="true">02</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="ben-row2">
        <div class="ben-card ben-card--c" role="listitem">
          <div class="ben-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="44" height="44" viewBox="0 0 44 44" fill="none"><path d="M22 10v8l5 5" stroke="#1a3a5c" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/><circle cx="22" cy="22" r="14" stroke="rgba(26,58,92,.4)" stroke-width="1.5"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="ben-card__title">Instalación simple</h3>
          <p class="ben-card__desc">Se instala bajo la pileta en menos de una hora. Te guiamos paso a paso por WhatsApp.</p>
          <div class="ben-card__num" aria-hidden="true">03</div>
        </div>
        <div class="ben-card ben-card--c" role="listitem">
          <div class="ben-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="44" height="44" viewBox="0 0 44 44" fill="none"><rect x="8" y="14" width="28" height="20" rx="8" stroke="rgba(26,58,92,.5)" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M16 22h12M22 18v8" stroke="#1a3a5c" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="ben-card__title">Protegé tus electrodomésticos</h3>
          <p class="ben-card__desc">El agua con menos minerales reduce la cal en cafeteras, hervidores y lavarropas.</p>
          <div class="ben-card__num" aria-hidden="true">04</div>
        </div>
        <div class="ben-card ben-card--d" role="listitem">
          <div class="ben-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="44" height="44" viewBox="0 0 44 44" fill="none"><rect x="14" y="10" width="16" height="24" rx="5" stroke="#2c6faa" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M20 28h4M22 10v-4" stroke="#5ba3d9" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="ben-card__title">Menos plástico</h3>
          <p class="ben-card__desc">Dejás de comprar botellas de un solo uso. Una pequeña acción con gran impacto ambiental.</p>
          <div class="ben-card__num" aria-hidden="true">05</div>
        </div>
        <div class="ben-card ben-card--e" role="listitem">
          <div class="ben-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="44" height="44" viewBox="0 0 44 44" fill="none"><path d="M22 8v8l6 3" stroke="rgba(0,200,224,.7)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/><circle cx="22" cy="22" r="14" stroke="rgba(0,200,224,.4)" stroke-width="1.5"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="ben-card__title">Disponible siempre</h3>
          <p class="ben-card__desc">Agua purificada 24/7 sin ir a comprar, sin esperar pedidos, sin quedarte sin stock.</p>
          <div class="ben-card__num" aria-hidden="true">06</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .benefits { padding: 88px 0; background: var(--white); }
  .benefits__header { max-width: 560px; margin-bottom: 64px; }
  .benefits__layout { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }
  .ben-row1 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr; gap: 2px; }
  .ben-row2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 2px; margin-top: 2px; }
  .ben-card {
    padding: 40px 36px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform .2s, box-shadow .2s;
  }
  .ben-card:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: var(--shadow-md); z-index: 1; }
  .ben-card--a { background: var(--blue-dark); color: var(--white); border-radius: var(--radius-lg) 0 0 0; }
  .ben-card--b { background: var(--surface); border-radius: 0 var(--radius-lg) 0 0; }
  .ben-card--c { background: var(--cyan); color: var(--blue-dark); border-radius: 0 0 0 var(--radius-lg); }
  .ben-card--d { background: var(--surface); }
  .ben-card--e { background: var(--blue-dark); color: var(--white); border-radius: 0 0 var(--radius-lg) 0; }
  .ben-card__icon { margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .ben-card__title { font-family: var(--font-head); font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.15rem; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .ben-card--a .ben-card__title,
  .ben-card--e .ben-card__title { color: var(--white); }
  .ben-card--b .ben-card__title,
  .ben-card--d .ben-card__title { color: var(--blue-dark); }
  .ben-card--c .ben-card__title { color: var(--blue-dark); }
  .ben-card__desc { font-size: .875rem; line-height: 1.65; }
  .ben-card--a .ben-card__desc,
  .ben-card--e .ben-card__desc { color: rgba(255,255,255,.7); }
  .ben-card--b .ben-card__desc,
  .ben-card--d .ben-card__desc { color: var(--text-muted); }
  .ben-card--c .ben-card__desc { color: rgba(26,58,92,.75); }
  .ben-card__num {
    position: absolute; bottom: 24px; right: 28px;
    font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: 4rem; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1;
    opacity: .08;
  }
</style>
